Quest PDF is a Chrome extension that helps you quickly find PDF files online by focusing your search specifically on PDF documents, making it easier to locate reports, manuals, and research papers without sifting through irrelevant results. Simply use ‘p’ + Space or ‘p’ + Tab in your Chrome address bar to start your search for PDF files instantly.

By clicking the “Add to Chrome” button, you accept and agree to install the ‘Quest PDF’ Chrome extension and set Chrome™’s default search to that provided by Yahoo!®. You also agree to the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. Please note that the search provided by Yahoo!® is active only when the user types ‘p’ + Space or ‘p’ + Tab in the address bar.


Privacy: https://questpdfapp.com/privacy/
TOS: https://questpdfapp.com/tos/
